metadata.name: Asian Triptych 001
metadata.description:
Asian Triptych 001 
This is the first in this collection! 
These are my homages to the Asian masters when masters were still creating masterpieces by exercising the skills they learned and developed after many years of training and practice.  Far beyond my skill set I used Ai assisted techniques to capture the essences of the masters and then hand corrected and embellished the final pieces for this collection.
